{"tid":34282,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(毒)有無人好怕講辭職??","createTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T01:22:39.000Z","uid":56758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d534a598b788fb9a463c465a856254e69199f9a","tid":34282,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"之前辭過一次<br />\n糾結左好耐先講到出口<br />\n不過個次就一個月內即日可以走<br />\n而家呢份返左半年又想辭職但諗起之後個一個月就覺得好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人都好怕開口辭職<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43ff210ed9c0b5263f28264d49da4d554691a06","tid":34282,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"有 怕醜到要叫人幫我講"},{"pid":"0781b658b13ba3c6a13d05b90cbb754a080cdb15","tid":34282,"uid":35955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"有 做左就快一年，教左我好多野<br />\nD野開始上手，驚一講就比佢屌我係養唔熟既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31671da4a9d7e309d30de06fb3ef62e2b6e6a945","tid":34282,"uid":38880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"想辭職已經半年，但係仲係講唔出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0152d3299e5da47457887b9c7634c95661d3c663","tid":34282,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 做左就快一年，教左我好多野<br />\nD野開始上手，驚一講就比佢屌我係養唔熟既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你搵到好路數，好既老細係會為你高興。<br />\n分分鐘你出去，第日有生意帶返比佢"},{"pid":"49eebddc54560723013f1682d67a775a6bb9005d","tid":34282,"uid":20270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 做左就快一年，教左我好多野<br />\nD野開始上手，驚一講就比佢屌我係養唔熟既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打工姐 你唔係真係以為自己係隻狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edb5ae2e8618d1656ca5cb29d979ebebbc535e2","tid":34282,"uid":35955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有 做左就快一年，教左我好多野<br />\nD野開始上手，驚一講就比佢屌我係養唔熟既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打工姐 你唔係真係以為自己係隻狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔係無用<br />\n佢當我係"},{"pid":"e862bd6e2fb716560a549816c993ec522ddf4c5b","tid":34282,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"其實同事都好肯教好好人<br />\n好似好辜負左人地一番心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9108a4809715fe2833b90006f0bef87c26bce6fa","tid":34282,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"有 未諗到點講"},{"pid":"bd3325878b3ae478ad6d07b9b2a25aaca1e7dd1a","tid":34282,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"On9先帶感情返工，你只係公司既肉便器"},{"pid":"02790d7fdd5b95afae8ab81a3e59ad46956be9f0","tid":34282,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9先帶感情返工，你只係公司既肉便器</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地搵個新人有幾難"},{"pid":"fe27541b5e3e25e576363f1f9ea96a2262fad459","tid":34282,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On9先帶感情返工，你只係公司既肉便器</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地搵個新人有幾難</blockquote><br />\n大家都係condom<br />\n但我真係覺得好唔好意思講<br />\n好撚on9啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61596db6b6878a1619b3ca4be995ba3243a51a68","tid":34282,"uid":4